<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Configure Solarwinds Notifications on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/scenarios/network-event-intelligence/4-configure-solarwinds-notifications/</link><description>Recent content in Configure Solarwinds Notifications on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/scenarios/network-event-intelligence/4-configure-solarwinds-notifications/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Install the Solarwinds Content Pack</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/scenarios/network-event-intelligence/4-configure-solarwinds-notifications/1-solarwinds-content-pack/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/en/scenarios/network-event-intelligence/4-configure-solarwinds-notifications/1-solarwinds-content-pack/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;In this section you will install and configure the SolarWinds Content Pack to ingest SolarWinds alerts into ITSI, completing the two-source alert pipeline needed for cross-vendor correlation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="callout callout--info"&gt;&lt;span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="callout__body"&gt;&lt;p class="callout__title"&gt;Exercise: Install the Solarwinds Content Pack&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1.&lt;/strong&gt; In ITSI, navigate to &lt;strong&gt;Configuration&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;gt; &lt;strong&gt;Data Integrations&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2.&lt;/strong&gt; Under the &lt;strong&gt;Alerts&lt;/strong&gt; section of the &lt;strong&gt;Integrations library&lt;/strong&gt;, select &lt;strong&gt;Solarwinds&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="callout callout--info"&gt;&lt;span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/&gt;&lt;line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/&gt;&lt;line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="callout__body"&gt;&lt;p class="callout__title"&gt;Info&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>